0119. W bran\u017cy Beauty i FMCG estetyka ma ogromne znaczenie!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, zarz\u0105dzanie kampani\u0105 PPC wymaga przemy\u015blanych dzia\u0142a\u0144 i ci\u0105g\u0142ego dostosowywania strategii. Pami\u0119taj, aby korzysta\u0107 z szerokiego dopasowania, ale z umiarem, oraz regularnie monitorowa\u0107 wyniki.<\/p>\n<p><i>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/i><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak skutecznie zarz\u0105dza\u0107 kampaniami PPC w kategorii Beauty i FMCG?<\/h1>\n<p>Planujesz uruchomi\u0107 <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3819,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3818","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kampanieppc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3818"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3818"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3818\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3819"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3818"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3818"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3818"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}